| Cast                    = [[File:Ant-Man (film) concept poster.jpg|right|thumb|SDCC exclusive concept poster]]
* {{WP|Paul Rudd}} as [[Scott Lang (Earth-199999)|Ant-Man / Scott Lang]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://marvel.com/news/movies/2013/12/19/21669/paul_rudd_set_to_star_in_marvels_ant-man|title=Paul Rudd Set to Star in Marvel's Ant-Man|work=Marvel.com|date=19 December 2013|accessdate=19 December 2013}}</ref><ref name="Douglas announcement"/> a thief hired by Hank Pym to break into Pym Technology and stop Darren Cross.

* {{WP|Evangeline Lilly}} as [[Hope Van Dyne (Earth-199999)|Hope Van Dyne]],<ref name="Comic-Con 2014">{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/07/ant-man-evangeline-lily-corey-stoll-marvel-comic-con/|title=Comic-Con: Evangeline Lilly & Corey Stoll Join 'Ant-Man' Stars As Marvel Screens Very Early Footage|last=Yamato|first=Jen|date=26 July 2014|accessdate=27 July 2014|work=Deadline}}</ref> the daughter of Hank Pym and Janet Van Dyne. Animosity between exists between her and her father over the Ant-Man suit being passed on to Scott Lang rather than her.<ref name="set visit">{{cite web|url=http://www.superherohype.com/features/344151-from-the-set-and-edit-bay-of-marvels-ant-man/|title=From the Set and Edit Bay of Marvel's Ant-Man|last=Perry|first=Spencer|work=SuperHeroHype!|date=22 June 2015|accessdate=23 June 2015}}</ref>

* {{WP|Corey Stoll}} as [[Darren Cross (Earth-199999)|Yellowjacket / Darren Cross]],<ref name="Comic-Con 2014"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/agentm/status/493200659152265217|title=Corey Stoll plays Darren Cross, aka Yellowjacket in #AntMan. He was Hank Pym's mentee before things got sour. #MarvelSDCC|last=Penagos|first=Ryan|date=26 July 2014|accessdate=26 July 2014}}</ref> the current CEO of Pym Technologies, rebranded as "Cross Technologies."<ref name="set visit"/>

* {{WP|Bobby Cannavale}} as [[James Paxton (Earth-199999)|Officer Jim Paxton]], Maggie's fiancé<ref name="Production Starts">{{cite web|url=http://marvel.com/news/movies/2014/8/18/23096/production_begins_on_marvels_ant-man|title=Production Begins on Marvel's Ant-Man|work=Marvel.com|date=18 August 2014|accessdate=19 August 2014}}</ref><ref name="Updated Synopsis">{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/stitchkingdom/status/529730133180317697/photo/1|title=Untitled photo|author=Stitch Kingdom|work=Twitter|date=4 November 2014|accessdate=8 November 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.esquire.com/entertainment/movies/interviews/a33816/bobby-cannavale-interview/|title=Bobby Cannavale on Danny Collins, Meeting Pacino and De Niro, and Joining Ant-Man|last=Zemler|first=Emily|work=Esquire|date=20 March 2015|accessdate=13 April 2015}}</ref>

